  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ダウンタウン熱血物語。くにおくんシリーズの傑作RPGアクション。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Play as Alex and Ryan and cross River City to fight street gangs and save your girlfriend from the hands of a bad guy named \"Slick.\" Improve your fighting experience by powering-up your characters in River City's shops, picking-up items for bonuses and using the trash bins and pipes you will find in its streets.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
